{"tid":1793874,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔唔係成日j WinterOnFire嫁咩 做咩有香港手足搞眾籌拍翻套但無人比錢？","createTime":"2019-12-22T17:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T08:49:06.000Z","uid":9394,"like":55,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ede981b88923c278add39f02112a525429a1db40","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/theedgeofliberty/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftheedgeofliberty%2F&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDzDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=937a954d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/theedgeofliberty/</a><br />\n//《2019：夏日宣言》是一部關於香港反送中抗爭的紀錄片電影。本片希望以有限的電影長度內，綜合由6月9號起，反送中運動的形成及抗爭過程，以<span style=\"color: red;\">非單元形式</span>，呈現給所有本地以及海外觀眾，更加了解事情的來龍去脈，讓世界作一個歷史性的參考。<br />\n<br />\n影片將透過不同的受訪者講述，還原重要事件及細節，重點帶出反送中運動的核心價值，香港人的創意性，全民抗爭升級，遍地開花，國際戰線等等。//<br />\n<br />\n運動一路以黎既紀錄片大部分都係用一次既行動做內容 但好少係成場運動去拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢次套戲就係用類似winter of fire既方式去描述成場運動<br />\n我好想幾十年後可以播條片比個仔睇 比佢睇到自由係靠上一代努力爭取翻黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都要令有付出既手足比世界記住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一百萬姐 抵到爛 籌旗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>宣傳片</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wjx4yzYgYPg&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWjx4yzYgYPg%26feature%3Demb_title&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDzDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=dce32be3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wjx4yzYgYPg&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>眾籌link</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/2019-%e5%a4%8f%e6%97%a5%e5%ae%a3%e8%a8%80-the-edge-of-liberty/?fbclid=IwAR145kpJKLvDU4LETH3lAwKHF14GnAYNJx22xVdPodivr4Ralx-9NmGNlh4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F2019-%25e5%25a4%258f%25e6%2597%25a5%25e5%25ae%25a3%25e8%25a8%2580-the-edge-of-liberty%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR145kpJKLvDU4LETH3lAwKHF14GnAYNJx22xVdPodivr4Ralx-9NmGNlh4&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDzDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=221d253f\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/2019-%e5%a4%8f%e6%97%a5%e5%ae%a3%e8%a8%80-the-edge-of-liberty/?fbclid=IwAR145kpJKLvDU4LETH3lAwKHF14GnAYNJx22xVdPodivr4Ralx-9NmGNlh4</a>"},{"pid":"3209557dd85da32dd73d4c3e747fb9771b62567a","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:02:15.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"5d60810323c52fabae82980026ff67673253ff98","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:02:27.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"0dd5c4ae6a7108db8f08865154938e2be408c3be","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:02:39.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"34ea0b2eec1938f9681758edbd26b602b5cce549","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:02:57.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"1814a3a9b70237f717e20b5e8173bcb779011b16","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:03:12.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"76602291da17caef84b828bdcf4fa0997efe14c0","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"7c6cf4fa2de0d619209bfd350945a924cdcba642","tid":1793874,"uid":285371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:03:40.000Z","msg":"Kickstarter 唔係己經籌過？"},{"pid":"6750ebaad0ad67fe054fa04cb460c2ce53e70dd7","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:03:44.000Z","msg":"革"},{"pid":"108531fdaa16b54d1c8e7a9702488eabae2b6dfd","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:03:57.000Z","msg":"命"},{"pid":"97d2326b23ecf4bc49d2d7cd002ad2eb00740fa6","tid":1793874,"uid":219736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:04:22.000Z","msg":"之前眾籌都係呢部電影？"},{"pid":"23b8987977429c2f6be31f9c7e5e42989820ed2f","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c6cf4fa2de0d619209bfd350945a924cdcba642","tid":1793874,"uid":285371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:03:40.000Z","msg":"Kickstarter 唔係己經籌過？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"籌過一次 fail左<br />\n所以我先幫佢地推<br />\n我唔想手足失望多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0de864061f4dcd7355944d1553fe4f1a04d948","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"97d2326b23ecf4bc49d2d7cd002ad2eb00740fa6","tid":1793874,"uid":219736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:04:22.000Z","msg":"之前眾籌都係呢部電影？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:07:44.000Z","msg":"//問：你們跟《催淚之城》有甚麼分別？<br />\n<br />\n答：當中最大分別是，《催淚之城》是做連續單元系列，而《2019: 夏日宣言》是一部90 - 120分鐘電影。《2019: 夏日宣言》主要以非線性形式，重點帶出反送中抗爭的價值，各項創舉，香港人的創意性文宣，Be water遍地開花，國際戰線等等。我們主要目標是將電影帶上國際影展，各地放映，以及Netflix/Amazon等串流平台。<br />\n<br />\n在此我們必需表示，我們《夏日宣言》團隊雖然跟《催淚之城》團隊有交流，但製作單位其實是兩班人。<br />\n不過大家同樣是愛香港，想貢獻香港的電影工作者。<br />\n<br />\n我們團隊早於6月11日開始拍攝，亦是是次運動中最早期的自發性攝製團隊（非電視台，非受薪，純自發，多機同步拍攝），比《催淚之城》團隊早。<br />\n<br />\n而在我們拍攝期間，亦有跟其他現場記者交流；<br />\n除我們以外，有多達雙位數以上的不同組織拍攝紀錄片。<br />\n<br />\n言而，這不是一個競賽，沒有比較不比較；<br />\n因為即使大家紀錄同一個事件，每一套紀錄片的角度，切入點，想表達及關注的地方，都不盡相同，這就是所謂的&quot;創作&quot;。相反，不同組織媒體相繼拍攝紀錄，讓反送中抗爭運動在國際關注度更高，我們團隊表示感激。<br />\n同時，我們表示支持《催淚之城》團隊。//<br />\n<br />\n唔知呢個答唔答到手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48336cbe365b4e35344201735d6d27c40adfa4ba","tid":1793874,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDzDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=6f650c60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"2d480c78a6fed7d1eb76cd97fabe4a2c6b0a8145","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"補充翻先<br />\n之前佢地已經聚籌過一次 但遠遠未夠達標<br />\n我個人認為果次宣傳係唔夠既<br />\n所以依家再籌要全力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好令有心手足失望兩次<br />\n最後附上佢地facebook既 Q&amp;A 比大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問：你們跟《催淚之城》有甚麼分別？<br />\n<br />\n答：當中最大分別是，《催淚之城》是做連續單元系列，而《2019: 夏日宣言》是一部90 - 120分鐘電影。《2019: 夏日宣言》主要以非線性形式，重點帶出反送中抗爭的價值，各項創舉，香港人的創意性文宣，Be water遍地開花，國際戰線等等。我們主要目標是將電影帶上國際影展，各地放映，以及Netflix/Amazon等串流平台。<br />\n<br />\n在此我們必需表示，我們《夏日宣言》團隊雖然跟《催淚之城》團隊有交流，但製作單位其實是兩班人。<br />\n不過大家同樣是愛香港，想貢獻香港的電影工作者。<br />\n<br />\n我們團隊早於6月11日開始拍攝，亦是是次運動中最早期的自發性攝製團隊（非電視台，非受薪，純自發，多機同步拍攝），比《催淚之城》團隊早。<br />\n<br />\n而在我們拍攝期間，亦有跟其他現場記者交流；<br />\n除我們以外，有多達雙位數以上的不同組織拍攝紀錄片。<br />\n<br />\n言而，這不是一個競賽，沒有比較不比較；<br />\n因為即使大家紀錄同一個事件，每一套紀錄片的角度，切入點，想表達及關注的地方，都不盡相同，這就是所謂的&quot;創作&quot;。相反，不同組織媒體相繼拍攝紀錄，讓反送中抗爭運動在國際關注度更高，我們團隊表示感激。<br />\n同時，我們表示支持《催淚之城》團隊。<br />\n<br />\n問：為何現在眾籌？<br />\n<br />\n答：其實團隊一開始並沒想過運動會發展至這樣龐大，當初只是預計約3個月左右。及後運動發展之規模已超出我們可應付範圍，團隊各人不眠不休地拍攝。我們開始討論要不要眾籌以增加人手，特別在處理後期工作上，花費不小。而我們不是有錢人，此project亦沒有投資者，我們只是一班想用自己專業技能為香港做點貢獻的電影工作者。早期我們把自己私下的資金都投放在器材上，往後可以動用的資金有限。<br />\n<br />\n另外，我們團隊一直在忙於拍攝的情況下，以及有關眾籌資金運用及個人資料保障問題需要詳細會議討論，需要時間達共識。同時，亦因為人手有限，包括導演也基乎每天在現場拍攝，所以遲遲未有出眾籌稿。當《催淚之城》的眾籌出現，我們團隊決定在不分簿他們達成目標下，直至讓他們的眾籌完了，我們才出，而我們團隊亦有課金支持《催淚之城》。<br />\n<br />\n我們眾籌比人遲，皆因我們全力應付前線拍攝，而錢不是我們首要考慮。直至現在進入後期階段，資金短缺的情況下，以及後期需要花費的已經超出我們能負擔的，希望各位有心人可以支持我們！感謝各位！<br />\n<br />\n問：紀錄片對運動有即時貢獻嗎？<br />\n<br />\n答：我們團隊的出發點是為了用自己專業技能為香港出一分力，明白紀錄片不能即時為運動帶來貢獻，因此，我們除了製作紀錄片而外，也透過其他工作去幫場運動，包括：網上直播、文宣poster、非商用影片提供、呈堂證據片(以證明手足沒涉及暴動及撒消控罪)、協助本屆多名港島區民主及本土派區議會候選人製作宣傳短片、協助BBC拍攝反送中紀錄片特輯，以及製作DGX團隊《不屈進行曲》MV等。<br />\n<br />\n問：你們有營利目的嗎？<br />\n<br />\n答：我們團隊為自發性組織，並不會從眾籌中牟利，全數將用作製作上。而事實上，製作一部電影，花費最重的部分，正正是後製階段，而拍攝的成本只是很有限，因為不是戲劇，沒有演員的關係，所以需要眾籌完成。<br />\n<br />\n但將來製作好後，成品會帶來盈利嗎？ 相信是有的，因為當網上平台如Netflix轉播你的電影時，就會給我們播放費，就像版權費一樣。若果有幸於各戲院上映，也會有票房收益的。<br />\n<br />\n不過，我們在眾籌內文亦表明，若有收益，會將部分捐給國際特赦組織，以及支援香港本地的電影業發展。"},{"pid":"260afee2763b7f06456203c9eca55d949f166e05","tid":1793874,"uid":61918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:15:59.000Z","msg":"出糧捐錢先"},{"pid":"15bd0adf661e9e8eb5277d941f1a47bbfd5fe5a6","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:16:16.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"aefeb3ddc62b039bd854256db183e5e1e597937f","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:16:27.000Z","msg":"大"},{"pid":"38ed6a0eb00f6702025e6f5efaf00b1a82889953","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:16:37.000Z","msg":"訴"},{"pid":"18f747c752eb3ad6e40ca63757b397504380a0e5","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:16:51.000Z","msg":"求"},{"pid":"e0be558e952dc0fc8bf7de8ce7f446c4c3c9408c","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:17:04.000Z","msg":"缺"},{"pid":"d5908caeb3ab4f406a3878e243e4e0d096981dc0","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:17:21.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"e942db45719b7aab01d2c282333ea346f0238f00","tid":1793874,"uid":3406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae475bc5e289a153070fd9a3785e8cb8ff32460","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:17:35.000Z","msg":"不"},{"pid":"6405c067d5fe3a83393d7224b6a2e0f3eb2a77ea","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:17:45.000Z","msg":"可"},{"pid":"eeceddd4d72270f97789f28cf673a778c15d5a3b","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"做咩負皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9699646e091856822ebb4a15f0ec1a7a204e8465","tid":1793874,"uid":46072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:27:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2081e3229363ca63e10c1dbd4bcf4ce7c3f9e69d","tid":1793874,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:30:59.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e37e05d22569736392268f020289445fdfaaa5","tid":1793874,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:35:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c9952dee9882bd29bed1fc7ad9052c37c2aafc5","tid":1793874,"uid":33556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3565e0424694e6c21aa81a0e271c1602a47dcda0","tid":1793874,"uid":42495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:43:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\